      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just so exhausting. the effort of having to pretend to be someone else, or even trying to find some new \"version\" of myself... it sounds like so much work. i'm just so tired of fighting to exist in a world where i've already lost. it feels like the most honest thing left to do is just stop fighting it. like, if the person i was is gone, why am i still even here pretending?",
